FBIS4-43845 "drweu120_o_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-120 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 CYPRUS Kliridhis Delays Corfu Departure; To Wait for Clark Kliridhis Delays Corfu Departure; To Wait for Clark NC2206091194 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in Greek 0900 GMT 22 Jun 94 NC2206091194 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network Greek BFN [Excerpt] The departure of President Glavkos Kliridhis for Corfu [planned for this afternoon] has been postponed until tomorrow due to the arrival of Joe Clark, the UN secretary general's special representative on Cyprus. Clark, who is expected to arrive in Cyprus late this afternoon, is carrying a letter from UN Secretary General Butrus Butrus-Ghali to President Kliridhis and Rauf Denktas on the confidence-building measures. [passage omitted]
